// SPDX-License-Identifier: BSD-4-Clause
/*
 * ABDK Math Quad Smart Contract Library.  Copyright © 2019 by ABDK Consulting.
 * Author: Mikhail Vladimirov <mikhail.vladimirov@gmail.com>
